DO YOU MEAN
HIM OR ME?

00:12:13.383 --> 00:12:14.943
HIM.
OH.

00:12:18.204 --> 00:12:20.204
Next: New New York in crisis.

00:12:20.273 --> 00:12:21.473
Morbo?

00:12:21.541 --> 00:12:22.907
Thanks, human female.

00:12:22.976 --> 00:12:24.871
Puny earthlings
were shocked today

00:12:24.895 --> 00:12:27.361
to learn that a ball of garbage
will destroy

00:12:27.431 --> 00:12:29.463
their pathetic city
of New New York.

