ON A SUPERCOMPUTER

00:12:42.245 --> 00:12:44.424
BUT THE BALL IS JUST
TOO DAMN GOOEY.

00:12:44.448 --> 00:12:46.581
A MISSILE WOULD GO
RIGHT THROUGH IT.

00:12:47.984 --> 00:12:51.453
BUT SUPPOSE WE SENT A CREW
TO PLANT AN EXPLOSIVE

00:12:51.521 --> 00:12:53.515
PRECISELY ON
THE FAULT LINE

00:12:53.539 --> 00:12:55.689
BETWEEN THIS MASS
OF COFFEE GROUNDS

00:12:55.758 --> 00:12:58.826
AND THIS DEPOSIT
OF AMERICA ONLINE FLOPPY DISKS.

