IN THEORY, IT COULD WORK.

00:13:03.149 --> 00:13:04.599
UH, IN THEORY, PERHAPS

00:13:04.667 --> 00:13:07.419
BUT YOU'LL NEVER FIND A CREW
WILLING TO TAKE ON A MISSION

00:13:07.471 --> 00:13:09.003
SO SUICIDALLY DANGEROUS.

00:13:10.957 --> 00:13:12.223
AW, CRAP.

00:13:12.291 --> 00:13:14.208
NOW YOU'LL ONLY HAVE
ONE CHANCE

00:13:14.277 --> 00:13:15.376
TO DESTROY THE BALL.

00:13:15.444 --> 00:13:16.761
AFTER THAT

00:13:16.830 --> 00:13:19.630
IT WILL BE SO CLOSE TO EARTH
THAT BLOWING IT UP

00:13:19.682 --> 00:13:22.716
WOULD CAUSE GARBAGE TO RAIN
OVER THE ENTIRE PLANET

00:13:22.785 --> 00:13:24.352
KILLING BILLIONS.

00:13:24.421 --> 00:13:25.719
AW, BOO-HOO.

00:13:25.788 --> 00:13:27.955
NOW HERE'S THE BOMB
I'VE PREPARED.

00:13:28.024 --> 00:13:29.304
ONCE YOU ACTIVATE IT

00:13:29.342 --> 00:13:31.525
YOU'LL HAVE 25 MINUTES
TO GET AWAY.

00:13:31.611 --> 00:13:32.727
THAT'S ALL? BUT...

00:13:32.796 --> 00:13:34.195
NOW, NOW.

00:13:34.264 --> 00:13:36.584
THERE'LL BE PLENTY OF TIME
TO DISCUSS YOUR OBJECTIONS

00:13:36.616 --> 00:13:37.731
WHEN AND IF YOU RETURN.

00:13:50.897 --> 00:13:51.957
ODOR AT MAGNITUDE EIGHT.

00:13:53.450 --> 00:13:54.450
MAGNITUDE 12.

00:13:55.818 --> 00:13:57.452
MAGNITUDE 31.

00:13:57.521 --> 00:13:58.987
<i>WE'RE BREAKING UP.</i>

00:13:59.055 --> 00:14:01.556
<i>TURN ON THE ANTI-SMELL DEVICE.</i>

00:14:03.760 --> 00:14:06.260
<i>HMM, SPORTY.</i>

00:14:09.599 --> 00:14:11.598
WOW!

00:14:11.667 --> 00:14:14.202
LOOK AT ALL THIS FILTH.

00:14:14.271 --> 00:14:15.951
IT'S NOT FILTH.

00:14:16.006 --> 00:14:17.572
IT'S A GLORIOUS MONUMENT

00:14:17.641 --> 00:14:20.308
TO THE ACHIEVEMENTS
OF THE 20th CENTURY.

00:14:20.377 --> 00:14:22.142
LOOK, A REAL BEANIE BABY.

00:14:22.211 --> 00:14:24.528
OH, A MR. SPOCK
COLLECTORS' PLATE.

00:14:25.598 --> 00:14:27.498
SOME BART SIMPSON DOLLS.

00:14:29.352 --> 00:14:31.502
Eat my shorts.

00:14:31.570 --> 00:14:33.354
OKAY.

00:14:33.423 --> 00:14:35.423
MMM, SHORTS.

00:14:35.491 --> 00:14:38.120
FRY, THIS STUFF
WAS GARBAGE WHEN
IT WAS NEW.

00:14:38.144 --> 00:14:39.655
LET'S BLOW IT
UP ALREADY.

00:14:39.679 --> 00:14:41.112
THIS JUNK ISN'T GARBAGE.

00:14:41.181 --> 00:14:42.847
I CAN DIG
IN ANY RANDOM PILE

00:14:42.915 --> 00:14:44.465
AND FIND
SOMETHING GREAT.

00:14:54.811 --> 00:14:56.694
ALL RIGHT,
LET'S GET TO WORK.

00:15:01.134 --> 00:15:03.751
LET'S SEE.

00:15:03.819 --> 00:15:05.603
IF THAT'S HYPODERMIC RIDGE

00:15:05.671 --> 00:15:07.922
THEN THE BOMB MUST GO
RIGHT HERE.

00:15:12.012 --> 00:15:13.021
GET READY TO RUN.

00:15:13.045 --> 00:15:14.312
WE'VE GOT 25 MINUTES.

00:15:14.380 --> 00:15:16.680
UH, 15 MINUTES.

00:15:16.749 --> 00:15:18.533
FIVE MINUTES.

00:15:18.602 --> 00:15:20.434
SIX-H MINUTES?

00:15:21.504 --> 00:15:23.438
HMM.

00:15:23.506 --> 00:15:25.640
THERE'S YOUR PROBLEM.

00:15:25.708 --> 00:15:28.860
THE PROFESSOR PUT
THE COUNTER ON UPSIDE DOWN.

00:15:28.928 --> 00:15:30.394
THAT IDIOT.

00:15:30.446 --> 00:15:32.229
IT WASN'T SET FOR 25 MINUTES.

00:15:32.298 --> 00:15:33.898
IT WAS SET FOR 52 SECONDS.

00:15:34.951 --> 00:15:36.317
WE'RE GOING TO DIE!

00:15:36.386 --> 00:15:37.666
RIGHT?
RIGHT.

00:15:44.844 --> 00:15:47.178
IT'S GOING TO BLOW!

00:15:50.116 --> 00:15:51.132
HEY, WATCH IT!

00:15:51.201 --> 00:15:52.744
YOU'LL PUT
SOMEBODY'S EYE OUT!

00:15:52.768 --> 00:15:54.696
OKAY, OKAY,
KEEP YOUR SPACE PANTS ON.

00:15:54.720 --> 00:15:56.880
I'LL TAKE CARE
OF THIS.

00:16:05.098 --> 00:16:06.414
WE'RE SAVED.

00:16:06.483 --> 00:16:09.433
YEAH, BUT THIS GARBAGE BALL'S
UNSTOPPABLE NOW.

00:16:09.502 --> 00:16:11.135
NEW NEW YORK IS DONE FOR.

00:16:16.726 --> 00:16:18.487
All in all, this is one day

00:16:18.511 --> 00:16:20.912
Mittens the kitten
won't soon forget.

00:16:23.883 --> 00:16:25.800
Kittens give Morbo gas.

00:16:25.869 --> 00:16:26.950
In lighter news

00:16:27.019 --> 00:16:29.587
the city of New New York is
doomed.

00:16:29.655 --> 00:16:33.858
Blame rests with known human
Professor Hubert Farnsworth

00:16:33.926 --> 00:16:36.010
and his tiny inferior brain.

00:16:36.078 --> 00:16:40.798
OH, HOW COULD I HAVE PUT
THAT BOMB TIMER ON UPSIDE DOWN?

00:16:40.867 --> 00:16:42.734
I COULD SWEAR I FOLLOWED

00:16:42.802 --> 00:16:44.552
THE MANUAL PRECISELY.

00:16:44.620 --> 00:16:47.304
I'M A DRIED-UP HUSK
OF A SCIENTIST.

00:16:47.373 --> 00:16:49.039
THIS IS ALL MY FAULT.

00:16:49.108 --> 00:16:50.608
NO, IT'S MY FAULT, TOO.

00:16:50.677 --> 00:16:52.009
I'M SURE I THREW OUT

00:16:52.078 --> 00:16:54.878
MORE THAN MY SHARE
OF THAT TRASH UP THERE.

00:16:54.947 --> 00:16:56.558
ALSO, ONE MONTH,
MY TOILET BROKE

00:16:56.582 --> 00:16:58.816
AND I JUST WENT
STRAIGHT IN THE GARBAGE CAN.

00:16:58.885 --> 00:17:00.351
AW!

00:17:00.420 --> 00:17:01.719
LEELA WAS RIGHT.

00:17:01.788 --> 00:17:05.156
THE PEOPLE OF
THE 20th CENTURY
WERE IDIOTIC SLOBS.

00:17:05.225 --> 00:17:06.490
ESPECIALLY ME.

00:17:06.559 --> 00:17:08.353
ENOUGH. YOU ALL
FAILED MISERABLY.

00:17:08.377 --> 00:17:10.610
IT'S TIME TO PUT
A REAL SCIENTIST IN CHARGE.

00:17:12.465 --> 00:17:13.363
WERNSTROM!

00:17:13.432 --> 00:17:14.731
THE VERY SAME.

00:17:14.800 --> 00:17:17.168
DR. WERNSTROM, CAN
YOU SAVE MY CITY?

00:17:17.237 --> 00:17:19.286
OF COURSE,
BUT IT'LL COST YOU.

00:17:19.355 --> 00:17:20.621
FIRST, I'LL NEED TENURE.

00:17:20.690 --> 00:17:21.472
DONE.

00:17:21.540 --> 00:17:22.757
AND A BIG RESEARCH GRANT.

00:17:22.825 --> 00:17:23.524
YOU GOT IT.

00:17:23.593 --> 00:17:24.642
ALSO ACCESS TO A LAB

00:17:24.710 --> 00:17:26.193
AND FIVE GRADUATE STUDENTS...

00:17:26.262 --> 00:17:27.861
AT LEAST THREE OF THEM CHINESE.

00:17:27.930 --> 00:17:29.580
ALL RIGHT, DONE.

00:17:29.649 --> 00:17:31.432
WHAT'S YOUR PLAN?

00:17:31.501 --> 00:17:32.716
WHAT PLAN?

00:17:32.785 --> 00:17:34.051
I'M SET FOR LIFE.

00:17:34.120 --> 00:17:36.186
AU REVOIR, SUCKERS.

00:17:36.255 --> 00:17:37.504
THAT RAT.

00:17:37.574 --> 00:17:38.856
DO SOMETHING.

00:17:38.925 --> 00:17:41.108
I WISH I COULD,
BUT HE'S GOT TENURE.

00:17:42.529 --> 00:17:44.009
EWW!

00:17:57.760 --> 00:17:59.293
IT'S TIME TO TAKE ACTION.

00:17:59.362 --> 00:18:01.595
STEPHANIE,
CANCEL THE MAID FOR TODAY.

00:18:01.663 --> 00:18:03.097
HAVE HER COME TOMORROW.

00:18:03.165 --> 00:18:04.860
WELL, I'M OUT
OF IDEAS.

00:18:04.884 --> 00:18:06.233
ANYONE?

00:18:06.302 --> 00:18:07.418
WAIT.

00:18:07.487 --> 00:18:09.303
IF WE COULD BUILD AN OBJECT

00:18:09.372 --> 00:18:10.938
THE EXACT SIZE, DENSITY

00:18:11.007 --> 00:18:13.106
AND CONSISTENCY
OF THE GARBAGE BALL

00:18:13.175 --> 00:18:15.425
IT MIGHT JUST KNOCK
THE BALL AWAY

00:18:15.494 --> 00:18:17.489
WITHOUT SMASHING
IT TO BITS.

00:18:17.513 --> 00:18:19.874
BUT WHERE CAN WE
FIND A SUBSTANCE

00:18:19.898 --> 00:18:23.050
THE EXACT DENSITY AND
CONSISTENCY AS GARBAGE?

00:18:23.118 --> 00:18:24.501
ALAS, I DON'T KNOW.

00:18:24.570 --> 00:18:26.487
UH, WHAT ABOUT GARBAGE?

00:18:26.555 --> 00:18:27.822
GOOD LORD!

00:18:27.891 --> 00:18:29.490
A SECOND BALL OF GARBAGE.

00:18:29.559 --> 00:18:30.892
THAT JUST MIGHT WORK.

00:18:30.960 --> 00:18:32.721
BUT GARBAGE
ISN'T SOMETHING

00:18:32.745 --> 00:18:35.162
YOU JUST FIND LYING
IN THE STREETS OF MANHATTAN.

00:18:35.248 --> 00:18:37.481
THIS CITY'S BEEN GARBAGE-FREE
FOR 500 YEARS.

00:18:37.550 --> 00:18:39.478
WELL, THEN IT'S TIME
TO MAKE SOME MORE.

00:18:39.502 --> 00:18:40.784
MAKE GARBAGE?

00:18:40.853 --> 00:18:42.102
BUT HOW?

00:18:42.171 --> 00:18:45.089
STAND BACK AND WATCH THE MASTER.

00:18:45.158 --> 00:18:47.341
THIS SLURM CAN...

00:18:47.409 --> 00:18:48.942
NOW IT'S GARBAGE.

00:18:49.011 --> 00:18:49.960
THESE PAPERS...

00:18:50.029 --> 00:18:51.128
GARBAGE.

00:18:51.197 --> 00:18:52.462
THIS PICTURE OF YOUR WIFE...

00:18:52.531 --> 00:18:54.164
PURE GARBAGE.

00:18:54.233 --> 00:18:56.149
NOW YOU TRY IT.

00:19:01.490 --> 00:19:03.890
BY GOD, I THINK
THE BOY'S GOT SOMETHING.

00:19:03.959 --> 00:19:05.137
COME ON, EVERYONE.

00:19:05.161 --> 00:19:07.172
THE FATE OF
THE CITY'S
AT STAKE.

00:19:07.196 --> 00:19:08.228
GOOD.

00:19:08.297 --> 00:19:09.574
DON'T FINISH
THAT CRULLER.

00:19:09.598 --> 00:19:10.547
THROW IT AWAY.

00:19:10.616 --> 00:19:11.665
BENDER, DRINK THAT BEER

00:19:11.734 --> 00:19:13.383
AND DROP THE BOTTLE
ON THE GROUND.

00:19:13.452 --> 00:19:14.735
VERY NICE.

00:19:14.804 --> 00:19:16.532
GET THAT ROBOT
SOME MORE BEER.

00:19:16.556 --> 00:19:17.571
HMM?

00:19:17.640 --> 00:19:18.683
WE'VE TRASHED THIS ROOM

00:19:18.707 --> 00:19:19.851
BUT THAT'S JUST A START.

00:19:19.875 --> 00:19:21.092
WE'VE GOT TO GET FRY'S

00:19:21.160 --> 00:19:22.409
MESSAGE TO THE PEOPLE.

00:19:22.478 --> 00:19:25.312
People of New New York

00:19:25.380 --> 00:19:27.631
take a lesson
from the 20th century...

00:19:27.700 --> 00:19:30.167
Stop all this
pain-in-the-ass recycling

00:19:30.235 --> 00:19:32.502
and throw your garbage
on the floor.

00:19:32.571 --> 00:19:35.689
Go ahead, just chuck it
any old place like I used to.

00:19:35.758 --> 00:19:37.541
Your city is counting on you.

00:19:49.171 --> 00:19:51.706
IF MY CALCULATIONS ARE CORRECT

00:19:51.774 --> 00:19:54.859
THIS GARBAGE BALL WILL KNOCK
THE OTHER GARBAGE BALL

00:19:54.927 --> 00:19:56.243
DIRECTLY INTO THE SUN.

00:19:56.311 --> 00:19:58.557
AND IF MY
CALCULATIONS
ARE CORRECT

00:19:58.581 --> 00:20:00.776
WE'RE ALL GOING
TO DIE HORRIBLY.

00:20:03.819 --> 00:20:05.369
ALL RIGHT, PLACES, EVERYONE.

00:20:05.438 --> 00:20:06.771
PREPARE FOR LAUNCH.

00:20:06.839 --> 00:20:11.275
FIVE, FOUR, THREE, TWO,

00:20:11.344 --> 00:20:15.295
THREE, FOUR, FIVE, SIX...

00:20:15.364 --> 00:20:17.448
JUST FIRE THE DAMN THING.

00:20:18.517 --> 00:20:20.901
OOPS.

00:20:53.018 --> 00:20:54.718
BURNING GARBAGE.

00:20:54.787 --> 00:20:56.036
IT WORKED!

00:20:59.041 --> 00:21:01.625
AND SO, ON BEHALF
OF THE ENTIRE CITY

00:21:01.693 --> 00:21:04.111
I THANK YOU,
PROFESSOR FARNSWORTH.

00:21:04.180 --> 00:21:06.296
I NOW PRESENT YOU
WITH THE ACADEMY PRIZE

00:21:06.365 --> 00:21:08.465
WHICH WE CONFISCATED
FROM DR. WERNSTROM

00:21:08.534 --> 00:21:11.068
AFTER IT BECAME APPARENT
THAT HE WAS A JACKASS.

00:21:12.521 --> 00:21:15.656
YES! IN YOUR FACE,
WERNSTROM!

00:21:15.725 --> 00:21:17.074
I'LL GET YOU, FARNSWORTH

00:21:17.142 --> 00:21:19.276
EVEN IF IT TAKES ANOTHER
HUNDRED YEARS.

00:21:20.712 --> 00:21:23.964
AND, FRY, WE OWE YOU
A TREMENDOUS DEBT AS WELL.

00:21:24.032 --> 00:21:27.367
WERE IT NOT FOR
YOUR 20th-CENTURY
GARBAGE-MAKING SKILLS

00:21:27.436 --> 00:21:30.287
WE'D ALL BE BURIED
UNDER 20th-CENTURY GARBAGE.

00:21:32.725 --> 00:21:34.908
SHOULD WE REALLY
BE CELEBRATING?

00:21:34.977 --> 00:21:36.688
I MEAN, WHAT IF
THIS SECOND GARBAGE BALL

00:21:36.712 --> 00:21:38.507
RETURNS TO EARTH
LIKE THE FIRST ONE DID?

00:21:38.531 --> 00:21:39.811
WELL, WHO CARES?

00:21:39.849 --> 00:21:42.716
THAT WON'T BE FOR
HUNDREDS OF YEARS.

00:21:42.785 --> 00:21:45.519
EXACTLY. IT'S NONE
OF OUR CONCERN.

00:21:45.588 --> 00:21:48.099
THAT'S THE 20th-CENTURY SPIRIT.

